# Build-Context-Hygiene fuer den Repo-Root-Build (packages/wot-vault/Dockerfile,
# context: . in .github/workflows/docker.yml). Vault braucht nur tsconfig.base.json
# + packages/wot-core + packages/wot-vault — alles Grosse/Irrelevante raus.
# (Greift NICHT fuer relay/profiles, deren Context = ihr Package-Dir ist.)
.git
**/node_modules
**/.turbo
**/dist
test-results
playwright-report
apps
*.log
